data.description: Price Adjusted for Immediate Sale! RESORT LIFESTYLE AT IT'S FINEST. Your family will feel like you're on a constant vacation in this gorgeous 2-YEARS YOUNG, 4 bedroom, 2 bath home located in The Willows at Sawgrass Lakes.  Features include gray quartz countertops, white cabinets, stainless steel appliances and ceramic simulated wood tile flooring throughout except bedrooms. Inside you'll find room for private and space for entertaining and family time. The beautiful lawn in the fenced yard is great for kids, the family pet and entertaining. Sawgrass Lakes have access to various community amenities, including a clubhouse, playground, pool, fitness center, and tennis courts. Scheduled social events occur regularly. Conveniently located close to I-95, Historic Melbourne Village and Melbourne. Int. Airport. (Rods and in Kitchen, office & front room, kitchen chandelier, entryway chandelier and washer and dryer do not convey.
